cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with improving the trajectory tracking performance of an industrial robot using neural networks and iterative learning control. The topic is closely related to robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as control systems (cs.SY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
